data.description: Stop here first!! This is a MOVE IN READY HOME! Completely renovated in 2021, upgrades include new windows, roof, siding, driveway, wrap around deck, fence, kitchen with granite countertops, baths, flooring, and fixtures. All appliances convey and are less than 2 years old. Brand new carpet on second floor (2023). Entire house was just pressure washed and front porch painted. Enjoy some cozy evenings around the fire pit in this nice fenced backyard! Great location, with a 5 minute drive to shipyards, Langley base 12 min drive. Close to major dining, shopping spots and interstates. This lovely home is ready for its new owners!
